{
  "stem": "5758.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Getting to Paris-- I didn't have much money in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to see the Eiffel Tower by, by Metro, saw loads and loads of German soldiers everywhere, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and went to see-- I went to see Champs-Elysees.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All by bus, I went around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My French was still not good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was not-- I could converse, but I had a terrible accent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Naturally, I was young.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But what does one thin when one is young-- women, nightlife.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I went to Place Pigalle, which was the center, all the cabarets and all the nightlife and nude shows and, and anything, you know, in this, in this field.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I came up the Metro on Place Pigalle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I noticed, again, full of Germans in, in uniform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I noticed there a tall fellow, Mediterranean-looking, talking to-- is around him, German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I went there to listen to him nearby.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and, I heard him say, you know, you have to see the, the, the cabaret, [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Eve ?] Cabaret with beautiful naked women dancing, and this here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he took a group and went down Pigalle, Rue Pigalle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was intrigued.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I followed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he took them to a cabaret, got them inside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I saw him to give the-- there was always a porter outside, you know, gave him a piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the, the soldiers went inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then he went back to Place Pigalle, speaking again to soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, that's interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That guy looks a little bit Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe, maybe he's a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said-- I went up to him and said, excuse me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I saw you talking to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Your German is pretty good.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
